  "_comment": "Curated Instagram POOL. Instagram blocks scraping, so permalinks are added by hand here. The hourly snapshot job re-randomises which posts show and in what order into instagram-feed.json (a fresh 'au hasard' mix each hour); the carousel renders from that. Each permalink renders as an on-brand tile that always paints and links out to the real post: it shows the post photo if src/data/ig/<shortcode>.jpg exists, otherwise a deterministic Armenian motif. To add a post: copy its URL (https://www.instagram.com/p/XXXXXXX/ or /reel/XXXXXXX/) into the matching account's `permalinks` array; optionally save its image as src/data/ig/XXXXXXX.jpg. Accounts with no permalinks yet show as a profile chip linking to Instagram.",
